The Pink Summer Sipper is a delightful and easy-to-make wine cocktail that features fresh strawberries, Chardonnay, sugar, and sparkling water. The result is a delicious and refreshing drink that is perfect for a relaxed Friday afternoon. The combination of fresh strawberries and Chardonnay creates a perfect balance of sweetness and acidity, while the addition of sparkling water adds a refreshing effervescence. Try this refreshing wine cocktail recipe at home, compliments of Spier. 